IN THE DARKNESS ♪

00:15.972 --> 00:19.889
♪ AFRAID TO STEP
INTO THE LIGHT ♪

00:20.020 --> 00:21.586
♪ SOME PEOPLE NEED

00:21.717 --> 00:23.545
♪ TO HELP SOMEBODY

00:23.675 --> 00:26.983
♪ WHEN THE EDGE
OF SURRENDER'S IN SIGHT ♪

00:27.114 --> 00:29.768
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY

00:30.465 --> 00:32.989
♪ IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT ♪

00:35.992 --> 00:37.820
♪ CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

00:37.950 --> 00:41.302
♪ I WON'T LET YOU
